<% text_for :title do %>
  You’ll need a visa to study in the UK
<% end %>

<% govspeak_for :body do %>
  The visa you apply for depends on your circumstances.

  <%= render partial: 'stateless_or_refugee', locals: {calculator: calculator} %>

  If you’re doing a short course or period of research, apply for a [Short-term Student visa](/study-visit-visa). You can study for up to 6 months, or up to 11 months on an English language course.

  If you’re coming to study for longer on a further or higher education course, apply for a [Student visa](/tier-4-general-visa).

  Or if you’re aged 4 to 17 and coming to study at an independent school, apply for a [Child student visa](/child-study-visa).
<% end %>
